OL,4,CLuke Mortimer: Aim to give Skipton boy
OL,5,Cwho lost limbs 'best life'
OL,6, Fundraising events have restarted to
OL,7, give a schoolboy who lost his hands and
OL,8, legs to meningitis the "best life
OL,9, possible" as he grows up.
OL,11,FLuke Mortimer, eight, was struck by a
OL,12,Frare strain of the disease in 2019.
OL,14,FDoctors had to amputate his arms below
OL,15,Fthe elbow and both legs below the knee
OL,16,Fwith Luke undergoing 23 operations.
OL,18,FThe family, from Skipton, said they
OL,19,Ffaced ongoing costs as Luke would need
OL,20,Fat least two sets of prosthetic arms
OL,21,Fand legs per year up to being 21.
